


		Optional Class

		as a java programmer we are familiar with NullPointerException
		java 8 has introduced a new optional class in java.util package this class can help in avoiding 
		 null checks and NullPointerExceptions
		you can view Optional as a single value container that either conatains value or doesn't
		it is said to be an empty
		
		Optional is a final class
		we can't extend
		